rlLocalizationActivelanguage.name: rlLocalizationActivelanguage
rlLocalizationActivelanguage.description: Points out to field rlLocalizationLanguagesName -- RG of the languages table. This value affects also translations performed on server side. -- RG not true If length is 0 this value is undefined; this means -- RG default language is applied.
